<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV78">
<l>cōrvilāta kātalāṟṟo ṭakkaṟāma ṉattarāy</l>
<l>nīrarāva ṇaikkiṭanta niṉmalaṉa laṅkaḻa</l>
<l>lārvamōṭi ṟaiñciniṉṟa vaṉpeyareṭ ṭeḻuttum</l>
<l>vāramāka vōtuvārkaḷ vallarvāṉa māḷavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who, with a [focused] manas—with attachment ceasing out of faultless love</l>
<l rend="indent">[for Him]—</l>
<l>affectionately prostrate themselves at the good feet of the blemishless [Lord]</l>
<l rend="indent">who lay on the serpent bed on the water,</l>
<l>and recite his eight-syllabled name with love,</l>
<l rend="indent">will be capable of ruling over heaven!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
